data.description: Spacious townhouse located in Liberty Hall Plantation.This property is in excellent condition and features two large bedrooms with en suite bathrooms. The primary bedroom has two closet!. As you enter this gorgeous home, you will enjoy the separate dining area ready for dinners and game nights. The large kitchen is situated off of the dining area which opens up to spacious living room. Perfect for entertaining! The screened porch offers a place to enjoy some outdoor time. Backyard is not currently fenced, but can be if desired. Did we mention the gorgeous hardwood floors throughout the downstairs. Community Pool is included in the Liberty Hall HOA!! Close toI-26, shopping, schools, restaurants and medical facilities.
